hopobject.body: Best Site good looking precio rebetol As ever there’s a raft of juicy cameos to enjoy, with Sarah Parish particularly pleasing as a giddily vain actress, and Patricia Hodge stern but sympathetic as a politically minded French scientist. Best of all, there’s a welcome wave of nostalgia when Poirot is reunited with old muckers Captain Hastings (Hugh Fraser), Miss Lemon (Pauline Moran) and Inspector Japp (Philip Jackson), who rally round in what might be Poirot’s darkest hour.
